Gun Runner - Spray and Pray
Smithy is deep undercover with arms dealer Darren Cutler, his nephew, Kieran Wallace, and Tommy Rose - a member
of the notorious SE1 gang. Rose shows Smithy a gun which he says has never been used. But Stevie, posing as Smithy&#039;s
girlfriend, sneaks it away and the officers trace it to a recent murder.
